---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
const metadata = {
  title: SITE_TITLE,
  description: SITE_DESCRIPTION,
};
---
<Layout {...metadata}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Society & AI Lab</h1>
    <p class="tagline">
      An independent research institute preparing humanity for the age of artificial general intelligence 
      through educational innovation. We explore how education systems must evolve to navigate the approaching 
      transformation of AGI, developing frameworks that embrace both the infinite potential of human creativity 
      and the systematic nature of learning.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Statement -->
  <section class="mission-section">
    <div class="mission-content">
      <h2>The Beginning of Educational Infinity</h2>
      <p>
        We stand at the threshold of humanity's greatest transformation. As artificial general intelligence approaches, 
        our educational systems—the engines of human knowledge creation—must undergo a fundamental reimagining. 
        The Society & AI Lab operates at this critical intersection, developing frameworks for educational evolution 
        that will define how humanity learns, adapts, and thrives in the AGI era.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Research Section -->
  <section class="research-section">
    <h2>Latest Research & Commentary</h2>
    <div class="research-articles">
      <div class="research-article">
        <h3>The New AI Literacy Framework: Preparing Students for an AI-Integrated World</h3>
        <p>By Dr. Sai Gattupalli | August 16, 2025</p>
      </div>
      <div class="research-article">
        <h3>Beyond the Hype: How AI Actually Transforms Teacher Workload and Professional Practice</h3>
        <p>By Dr. Sai Gattupalli | August 17, 2025</p>
      </div>
      <div class="research-article">
        <h3>SDG 4 as the Meta-Goal: Why Education Unlocks All Other Sustainable Development</h3>
        <p>By Dr. Sai Gattupalli | August 10, 2025</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Focus Areas Section -->
  <section class="focus-areas-section">
    <div class="focus-areas-container">
      <h2>Research Streams</h2>
      <div class="focus-areas-grid">
        <div class="focus-area">
          <h3>AI-Enhanced Learning Systems</h3>
          <p>Developing frameworks for AI as a Socratic partner in education—not replacing human thinking but catalyzing deeper understanding. We explore how AGI can guide learners through cycles of conjecture, criticism, and refinement to create better explanations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-area">
          <h3>Educational Systems Transformation</h3>
          <p>Mapping education as a complex adaptive system with multiple feedback loops and leverage points. We identify where small interventions—like AI tutors or personalized learning paths—can create systemic transformation across entire educational ecosystems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-area">
          <h3>The Resilience Curriculum</h3>
          <p>Building educational frameworks that prepare learners for radical uncertainty. We focus on meta-learning, cognitive flexibility, and emotional resilience—the core competencies needed to navigate continuous change in an AGI-transformed world.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-area">
          <h3>Global Education Intelligence</h3>
          <p>Creating open-source tools and frameworks that scale quality education to billions. Our research connects SDG 4 (Quality Education) as the master key that unlocks human potential to solve all other global challenges.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Approach Section -->
  <section class="approach-section section">
    <h2>Our Operating Principles</h2>
    <div class="principles-grid">
      <div class="principle">
        <h3>Problems Are Solvable Through Education</h3>
        <p>Every challenge facing humanity—from climate change to inequality—is fundamentally a knowledge problem. Education creates the problem-solvers who will address these challenges.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <h3>Systems, Not Silos</h3>
        <p>Following systems thinking principles, we recognize education as a complex adaptive system with stocks (knowledge), flows (learning processes), and feedback loops that can be optimized for transformation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <h3>The Power of Good Explanations</h3>
        <p>We develop educational frameworks that foster the creation of hard-to-vary, testable explanations—the foundation of all scientific and social progress in the age of AGI.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Impact Section -->
  <section class="impact-section">
    <h2>SDG 4: The Leverage Point for Human Progress</h2>
    <p>
      While the UN's 17 Sustainable Development Goals represent humanity's shared challenges, we recognize 
      SDG 4 (Quality Education) as the meta-goal—the leverage point that enables all others. Through education, 
      we create the problem-solvers who will address poverty, climate change, inequality, and every other 
      challenge we face. Our research demonstrates how AI-enhanced education can create a positive feedback 
      loop of accelerating human capability.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Commons Section -->
  <section class="commons-section">
    <p>
      The Society & AI Lab operates as a Scholarly Commons for education-centered AI research and deployment, 
      ensuring that the transformation of human learning remains a shared endeavor guided by collective wisdom 
      and global cooperation.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FAFAF6 0%, #F5F5F0 100%);
  }
  
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 5vw, 72px);
    color: #1a365d;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  
  .hero .tagline {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: #2d3748;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .mission-section {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .mission-content {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: #1a365d;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .mission-content p {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #4a5568;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  
  .research-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #FAFAF6;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  .research-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: #1a365d;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-top: 0;
    border-left: 4px solid #003A70;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }
  
  .research-articles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
  
  .research-article {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    width: 100%;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  
  .research-article:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    border-color: #003A70;
  }
  
  .research-article h3 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: #1a365d;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  
  .research-article p {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: #718096;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  
  .focus-areas-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003A70 0%, #002850 100%);
    padding: 5rem 0;
    margin: 4rem 0;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  
  .focus-areas-container {
    max-width: 1300px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: white;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  .focus-areas-container h2 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: white;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  
  .focus-areas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .focus-area {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .focus-area:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }
  
  .focus-area h3 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  
  .focus-area p {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  
  .approach-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #FAFAF6;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  .approach-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: #1a365d;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .principles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .principle {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .principle h3 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: #003A70;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .principle p {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: #4a5568;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .impact-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F7FAFC 0%, #EDF2F7 100%);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    margin: 4rem 0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .impact-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: #1a365d;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .impact-section p {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #2d3748;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  
  .commons-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
    margin: 4rem auto;
    max-width: 1100px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  
  .commons-section p {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }
    
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
    }
    
    .hero .tagline {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .focus-areas-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .principles-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>